Aedonmansa	An Aedonite holiday observed on Decander 24 in the calendar of Osten Ard.
Aedontide	A time of celebration for the birth of Usires Aedon.
Candlemansa	An Aedonite holiday observed on Feyever 2, transposed with Elysiamansa in the calendar notes.
Feyever	The second month of the Aedonite calendar, following Jonever and preceding Marris.
